\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Your project - research-oriented university system. You should have classes (superclasses, subclasses, abstract classes), interfaces, enumerations, your own exceptions, patterns (to be studied next week), etc. - all techniques we have studied. Before coding you must design your system - create an architecture using 
\f0\b Use Case 
\f1\b0 and 
\f0\b UML class Diagrams.
\f1\b0 \
\
Your project costs 30 points - 10 pts in ATT2 
\f0\b and
\f1\b0  20 of your final exam (other 20 points - oral exam. Team leaders automatically take 20 for this part).\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl280\partightenfactor0

